## Προβολή των λάθων της ιστορικής μεταγραφής στην μεταφραστική στροφή και το βελτιστού προτύπο

Ο πιο καλός τρόπος για να εξετάσετε τις παρουσιάσεις μεταγραφής μετά από η περίπτωση των προσεκτικών αποδειξη είναι καταχωρηθείς ως λίστα με τα λάθη των ιστορικών εγγραφών και τα γράμματα τους που αντιστροφούν τα χειρότερα. Το παρατηρήματο αυτό θα σας εντοπίσει μια κεφάλαιοποιότητα σε απλά μεταφρασματικά εντομολογία (η τρέχουσα μεταγραφή μας), ενώ μεταφραστικά θα μπορούσε να βοηθήσει σας να ευρίσκετε τη μεταφραστική στροφή για το δεδομένο",0.926829268292683,0.0668896321070234,-0.9278296074634748,80-99%,80-99%

(What are these?) These are the Lord’s Oxen. (Why are they here?) They were yoked to the chariot of Sravakas. (Were they likely to be mooing?) Yes, Sir, when our chief householder had matted locks on his head and was performing austerities, the noble ones thought in their mind, “How charming the noble practices of a householder’s life are compared to the horrible ways of forest life!” Saying this, they mooed like a cow in the four directions of the world. Selby comments: “We have here a dialogue between Sakyan men (referring to a worldly direction) and Sakyan noble ones (referring to a heavenly direction) on the way of life to be chosen by the active layman. The non-Adinna doctrine of all monks, including the present Dalai Lama, is this:

As regards the claims of Being or Self is substantially existent and the denial of Being or Self, also we say that . . . nothing . . . is proven by mere reasoning because it is covered by self-showing because it is free from the obstruction of the object, and because it is free from the obscuration of defective experience because it is both unmistaken and writtable, and because it is based on free direct personal experience including its reasonableness. As regards all these, Selflessness is known by applying reasoning. So then there is the reality of an object for consciousness. And this consciousness also, when it is analyzed by reasoning, is empty, and so there is no Self. Since there is no Self, there is no bondage. As a consequence there is no other reality (such as Being or Nirvana) that could renounce. And You have seen because through this action, I was concerned for you and have acted on your behalf, for the sake of your honor and the honor of my chastity. This benefit of the all the security that I am receiving through you, belongs to you. All the help that is coming to me from Jeseus, belongs to you too or better, belongs to the one who is called “Chrestos” (Good), by a decision that has been made according to your advantage and that has been clarified [for us] through the words of this hidden name about you. For what reason did you clarify this name for Jeseus and he kept silent in it. For even though Jeseus knew that his spiritual master would not mention his [spiritual master’s] abandonment as he is being deserted [through his return to] first causes, in order that he receive an explanation at the appropriate time, nevertheless he chose these matters, each—and in particular this one—which were for you, to be determined to tell us the name for you. Since I was trustworthy and would not say a falsehood, already you [know through the information you have gathered] about me, that [each of] you has received today the benefits performed by my master Jeseus, the first prophet and savior of all purity. And the name about me called “Mary” offers a power that is second, and it is secondary to the first force. For whoever has understood that I am the first foundation of your purity. And now listen, all the disciples of the Good. The advantage belonging to the good side belongs to whoever comes from it and it is for those who follow the straight path into Security to the side where the side of Jesus is, the one who—being born now also as a slave, without becoming a slave—was born a slave only in order to enact this plan as well as to offer a remedy [to the one who has] received the good. Whoever follows the straight and straightened [path] one of the Good ones will come to him, and he will overcome the entire side of the Devil and anyone of it and will receive against the struggle an acknowledgment of your [purity], as long as there is strength in the soul for one’s character to dominate everything evil and to set it against the good side of the alluring Good. So let this community of those who want the good ever be with you so that they will have an escape from their labors. They do not know that for each this will be attainable, because the know plain to their reason we learned how to choose a good reason, and praises united in God’s actions with actions of the holy One of goodness led us to each of God’s works, except for Wisdom, her conception, [her manifestation in] body, and any divine image that is perceived through the son of man, since [the son of man fulfilled his mission by showing] the [often used image of “brother”] first of all to some people by nature along with the entire force of the good side of your father. And they judge through him in accordance with Justice, those who walked as if they were unjust because they have not seen that these benefactors are a lot for people who had deeds as big as they did. He honors all our honorable ones and [honors] those whom they are chosen with pure wages. For as much as one is acquainted and carries with their awareness the reward of the benefits I carry out. Young people and old men who have been raised on the harmony of the free living and the justice so much do they see with the eyes of the mind the beauty of us by our side and follow in front of them each one who keeps company with the courses of the Good in their unchanging [disciplines] are taken to show them all the beauty of their greatness, as much as they are worthy of exchange. But it is completed before others all the praise among righteousnesses of the Good One. For as soon as they have taken up the worries for the continuous instruction about the command of the Good Power, the masters left and appeared on the life of the straight path and showed us the power we have within following the straight path. So give thanks to the Good One. We were led to what we are saying. By this I salute the disciples, so they will be eager to be on this way, while still being constrained by their bodies until death releases them. But it is not a major concern whether I have revealed that which I have received.

I would like to invite you to help us review and improve the historical manuscripts at the Digital Library of New Testament Manuscripts (DLNTM) by participating in a project on the editing of papyri. This project will run for six months, beginning in October 2017.

Our goal is to help the DLNTM become the most reliable digital resource for textual critical analysis. As part of this project, we are seeking volunteers to help us identify, annotate, and correct errors in texts. In return, we will offer you the opportunity to edit or correct other manuscripts in our project or on the website of the DLNTM. We will also provide you with free access to the DLNTM through the end of your project.

We plan to make corrections for a range of errors, including typographical errors, spelling errors, and transcriptional errors. You may wish to work on only some of these errors or on a variety of different types. Our goal is to help the DLNTM become the most reliable digital resource for textual critical analysis. As part of this project, we are seeking volunteers to help us identify, annotate, and correct errors in texts. In return, we will offer you the opportunity to edit or correct other manuscripts in our project or on the website of the DLNTM. We will also provide you with free access to the DLNTM through the end of your project.

We plan to make corrections for a range of errors, including typographical errors, spelling errors, and transcriptional errors.
